-EJERCICIO 6-

g8=mosaicCalc::D(cos(2*t^2) ~ t&t&t&t)
g8
## function (t) 
## -((cos(2 * t^2) * (2 * 2) - sin(2 * t^2) * (2 * (2 * t)) * (2 * 
##     (2 * t))) * (2 * 2) - (sin(2 * t^2) * (2 * (2 * t)) * (2 * 
##     2) + ((cos(2 * t^2) * (2 * (2 * t)) * (2 * (2 * t)) + sin(2 * 
##     t^2) * (2 * 2)) * (2 * (2 * t)) + sin(2 * t^2) * (2 * (2 * 
##     t)) * (2 * 2))) * (2 * (2 * t)) + (cos(2 * t^2) * (2 * 2) - 
##     sin(2 * t^2) * (2 * (2 * t)) * (2 * (2 * t))) * (2 * 2) + 
##     (cos(2 * t^2) * (2 * 2) - sin(2 * t^2) * (2 * (2 * t)) * 
##         (2 * (2 * t))) * (2 * 2))
curve(g8,c(0,5))

Solución 6.a: C)= Un coseno cuya amplitud crece y cuyo periodo decrece. Solución 6.b: C)= Cos, sin, squaring, multiplication and addition.
